snippet.title: Butler Until Midnight - Opening Movie [Voltage]
snippet.description:
Brand new, short walk to the subway and sunny...
And comes with a personal butler!?

◆Story◆

You've moved into an apartment that comes with attractive butlers?!

Hot tea,silky linens
these men are here for you...
 
You would never guess what they're hiding beneath the elegant smiles!
"Not all butlers are saints, you know..."
Your emotions are at the mercy of your butler as you begin a new life in the apartment of your dreams.

★Love 365 at the App Store★
